---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for CHEM-IS-TRY, Inc. – how we collect, use, and protect your information.">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>How we collect, use, and protect your information</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-content" style="max-width:860px;">

      <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>CHEM-IS-TRY, Inc. ("we", "our", "us") collects information you voluntarily provide when you contact us, submit a Request for Quotation, or otherwise communicate with us. This may include your name, company name, email address, phone number, and the details of your inquiry.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide quotations</li>
        <li>To fulfill orders and provide customer support</li>
        <li>To send relevant product or service updates (you may opt out at any time)</li>
        <li>To improve our website and services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. We may share information with trusted service providers (e.g., shipping carriers, payment processors) solely to fulfill your order or request. All such parties are obligated to keep your information confidential.</p>

      <h2>Confidentiality</h2>
      <p>CHEM-IS-TRY, Inc. treats all customer and project information as strictly confidential. We will not disclose any customer information, synthesis details, or proprietary processes without written consent. Non-disclosure agreements are available upon request.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>Our website uses Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our site. Google Analytics collects anonymized usage data (pages viewed, session duration, etc.). No personally identifiable information is transmitted to Google Analytics. You may opt out using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of personal information we hold about you by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@chem-is-try.com">info@chem-is-try.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions regarding this Privacy Policy should be directed to:</p>
      <p>
        CHEM-IS-TRY, Inc.<br />
        160-4 Liberty Street, Liberty Corporate Park<br />
        Metuchen, NJ 08840, USA<br />
        <a href="mailto:info@chem-is-try.com">info@chem-is-try.com</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
